{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"西班牙人民反抗之歌","authors":["贤治"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":2,"day":20}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"西班牙人民反抗之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下面几首民歌，是从《西班牙新的反抗之声》选译的。这些歌在西班牙人民中流传，它们表达了西班牙广大人民对弗朗哥反动政权的控诉和对自由、解放的向往。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西班牙的花朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西班牙的花朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在四月里开放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它没有带来欢乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它只带来了忧伤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年的战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年啊，岁月好悠长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对着统治者的枪口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民顽强地反抗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西班牙的花朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再不忍吐芬芳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为西班牙人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在四月里死亡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花儿终于又含苞了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摧残鲜花的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪能知道年年四月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花总要来到世上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西班牙的人民啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决不会甘心死亡！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪口杀不尽人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也阻止不了鲜花开放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从佛朗哥……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从佛朗哥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用链条锁住西班牙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们成了下贱的奴隶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再也找不到自己的国家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我亲爱的妈妈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不愿在这儿生活啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这么多的神父教士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪有地方留给我住下？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色胡子的上帝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你帮助我度过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阴森的西班牙夜晚吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明来到的时刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们会重见自由的祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时候，自由的风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会吹遍了西班牙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌云和希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上密布乌云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见一颗星星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷声夹着闪电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"预告风暴来临。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是暴风雨的时刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带来眼中的泪影。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空变得晴朗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有颗星在闪光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的光芒耀眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人对它向往。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是晴朗的时刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带来心头的希望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔贤治译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}